
Configuration is done in worldserver.conf


ChatCensor.Enabled  	: you can enable or disable the Censor function.

ChatCensor.BadnessLevel	: This is a trigger value
						  each word have a level for badness in database.
						  If a user using more as one bad word in one string, the level's are added.
						  If this added values is => BadnessLevel the string is replaced by warning.

Bad words Database		: table 'censor_bad_words' located in world database.
